        public static void lockdown()

        This allows container-like environments to prevent client messing with plugins.

      • setFillInOutsideLifecycleExceptionStacktraces

        public static void setFillInOutsideLifecycleExceptionStacktraces(boolean fillInStacktrace)
        Parameters:
        fillInStacktrace - true to fill in stacktraces in OutsideLifecycleExceptions. false to disable them (and use them as signals only). Disabling them, if you don't care about the stacktraces, can result in some minor performance improvements.
